{"data":[{"date":"20:25 14/06","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 14/6: M.U nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c m\u1eebng t\u1eeb Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/19/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-146-mu-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-tu-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 14/6.\r\n</h2><h2>M.U nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c m\u1eebng t\u1eeb Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u1edd b\u00e1o qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson Becker \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gia nh\u1eadp Los Blancos v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70-80 tri\u1ec7u euro. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a, M.U kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai David De Gea &ndash; m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng n\u0103m c\u1ee7a K\u1ec1n K\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 146 MU nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c m\u1eebng t\u1eeb Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 146 MU nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c m\u1eebng t\u1eeb Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/23/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-146-MU-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-tu-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 14/6: Real chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Salah \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">heo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp Hector Cuper, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mohamed Salah &ldquo;g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 100% k\u1ecbp ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Uruguay&rdquo;. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c nhanh h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng tin r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng m\u1eebng cho \u0110T v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Ai C\u1eadp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ee5 Martial</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Ph\u00e1p x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chia tay Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1ef1 tin gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n t\u1ef1 gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Martial.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u Premier League \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c FA c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Unai Emery s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n 2 nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t trong 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ea1i cho t\u00e2n HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, khi Arsenal \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o Top 4 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Unai Emery trinh bay ro viec tan dung nhung cai ten san co.\" title=\"HLV Unai Emery tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y r\u00f5 vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1eb5n c\u00f3.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/25/unai-emery-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea ngay 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nH\u00f4m nay, Lopetegui ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;N\u1ed7i h\u1ed5 th\u1eb9n&rdquo; c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha &ndash; HLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft &ldquo;s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn&rdquo; v\u1edbi K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n sa th\u1ea3i sau khi \u0111i \u0111\u00eam v\u1edbi Los Blancos, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 ng\u00e0y l\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3624","checkdouble":"188496"},{"date":"18:16 14/06","title":"Chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro, Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/23/real-madrid-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-thu-mon-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Mundo Deportivo c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Alisson</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi thay Navas. David de Gea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. HLV Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay Zidane, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0a De Gea v\u1ec1 Bernabeu.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 80 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/Real-Madrid-mua-Alisson-thanh-cong-voi-gia-80-trieu-euro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLopetegui t\u1eebng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft De Gea v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i U21 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, trong th\u1eddi gian d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0110T TBN \u00f4ng c\u0169ng lu\u00f4n \u01b0u ti\u00ean ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c De Gea \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Real Madrid.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Mundo Deportivo tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 Real Madrid mua Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Roma.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh sinh n\u0103m 1992, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Alisson k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Real, anh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 200.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u1edf Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real ph\u1ea3i chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Alisson</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng theo Mundo Deportivo, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 26 tu\u1ed5i. V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Roma \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Ederson \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Alisson\" title=\"thu mon Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/23/real-madrid-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-thu-mon-moi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 80 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Alisson \u0111ang c\u00f9ng \u0110T Brazil tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018, anh s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu sau khi h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Selecao \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEderson \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Roma. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 26 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Navas.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nho-thuyet-khach-liverpool-sap-co-thu-mon-moi-172-187344.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Alisson</span>, song h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 80 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u00e0 Roma y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. Real Madrid ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil khi \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3623","checkdouble":"188491"},{"date":"18:32 14/06","title":"Messi: \u201cBarca c\u1ea7n Griezmann \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/6/messi-barca-can-griezmann-de-thong-tri-chau-au.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn x\u1ee9 Catalonia trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/griezmann-len-ke-hoach-thong-bao-tuong-lai-nhu-phim-bom-tan-180-188470.html\" target=\"_blank\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Antoine Griezmann</span> kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cao s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay Atletico Madrid trong phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 2018 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ea3 tr\u0103m tri\u1ec7u Euro, sau nhi\u1ec1u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5p th\u1ecfm chuy\u1ec7n \u0111i \u1edf v\u00e0 b\u1ea1t ng\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi n\u0103m qua \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 chi\u1ebfu c\u1ed1 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u00ec t\u00ecnh ngh\u0129a v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n b\u1ecb FIFA c\u1ea5m chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Griezmann \u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Barca v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch C\u00fap C1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Messi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Griezmann \u0110i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 Barca v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch C\u00fap C1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/6/messi-moi-goi-griezmann-den-voi-barcelona.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Griezmann: \"Barca c\u1ea7n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League\"</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfm th\u1ebf th\u01b0\u1ee3ng phong h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 Man Utd m\u00e0 thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh Barcelona. \u0110\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i, k\u00e9o theo h\u00e0ng t\u00e1 l\u1eddi m\u1eddi ch\u00e0o h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn anh c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou t\u1eeb n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u01b0 c\u1ee7a Luis Suarez hay hai \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Ousmane Dembele v\u00e0 Samuel Umtiti.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t Leo Messi \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Griezmann s\u1edbm v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina v\u1ec1 tham v\u1ecdng t\u00e1i th\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecb Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u1ee7a Barca sau khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ef1u t\u00e0i n\u0103ng Real Sociedad trong tay:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu Barca c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Griezmann th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League th\u00eam n\u1eefa v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft Griezmann c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Barca hay kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu t\u00f4i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c trong ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB, anh bi\u1ebft c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi r\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea5y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Messi n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Griezmann. Hai ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Argentina v\u00e0 Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 ngay v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi n\u1ebfu hai \u0110TQG v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t nh\u00ec so le nhau.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/griezmann-da-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-180-188330.html\">Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t xong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, nh\u01b0ng\u2026</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/griezmann-len-ke-hoach-thong-bao-tuong-lai-nhu-phim-bom-tan-180-188470.html\">Griezmann l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai... nh\u01b0 phim bom t\u1ea5n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chu-tich-la-liga-bao-tin-vui-cho-thanh-madrid-tin-buon-cho-barca-180-188224.html\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch La Liga b\u00e1o tin vui cho th\u00e0nh Madrid, tin bu\u1ed3n cho Barca</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3622","checkdouble":"188495"},{"date":"05:28 15/06","title":"Lopetegui b\u1eadt kh\u00f3c trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/lopetegui-bat-khoc-trong-ngay-ra-mat-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00fang v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga di\u1ec5n ra tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c World Cup 2018 gi\u1eefa Nga vs Saudi Arabia, th\u00ec t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Real Madrid t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o quan tr\u1ecdng ra m\u1eaft t\u00e2n HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Julen Lopetegui.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">M\u1edf m\u00e0n bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez n\u00f3i: \"Th\u1ef1c ra, Cch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0y sau khi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> k\u1ebft th\u00fac, khi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vinh quang. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp x\u1ea3y ra m\u1ea5y ng\u00e0y qua, th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1edf ra trang m\u1edbi v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \"Madridista\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c Real k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf ra v\u1edbi Lopetegui t\u1ea1i Madrid.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Lopetegui ra m\u1eaft Real v\u00e0 n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Lopetegui ra m\u1eaft Real v\u00e0 n\u00f3i g\u00ec h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Real-Madrid-present-new-coach-Julen-Lopetegui.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh c\u00f9ng t\u00e2n hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean Lopetegui. \u1ea2nh: Reuters.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, Lopetegui cho bi\u1ebft t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n HLV t\u1ea1i Bernabeu: \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 trong kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ng\u00e0y m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Real kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft n\u00f3i: \u201cSau khi m\u1eb9 t\u00f4i qua \u0111\u1eddi, vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eadn tin b\u1ecb \u0110TQG sa th\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y bu\u1ed3n nh\u1ea5t trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi t\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00f4m nay l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac nh\u1ea5t\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi b\u1ecb h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do sa th\u1ea3i li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 li\u00ean quan g\u00ec t\u1edbi l\u00fd do chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n hay kh\u00f4ng, Lopetegui t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00e0 cho hay kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra. Tuy nhi\u00ean, hi\u1ec7n \u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i khi c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\"T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Rubiales (ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN) h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng ki\u1ec3u kh\u00e1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n trung th\u1ef1c v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi khi th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn (gia nh\u1eadp Real) \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng khai v\u00e0 che gi\u1ea5u n\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea5u. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 trung th\u1ef1c h\u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3\", Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: \"Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi s\u1ebd v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebfn r\u0169 c\u1ee7a Real Madrid\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ef1u HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. Hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tho\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7. Do \u0111\u00f3, \u00f4ng m\u1ed9t m\u1ef1c ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch cho r\u1eb1ng Real \u0111\u00e3 \"\u0103n tr\u1ed9m\" Lopetegui v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c v\u00f4 l\u00ed. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3621","checkdouble":"188509"},{"date":"06:04 15/06","title":"Ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n CLB c\u1ee7a Griezmann m\u00f9a t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/17/griezmann-da-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Antoine Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Th\u00f4ng qua m\u1ed9t \u0111o\u1ea1n video ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n r\u00e2m ran</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Antoine Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi trong nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ng qua. T\u1eeb l\u00fac b\u00e1o ch\u00ed khui ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea1i gia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong \u0111\u00f3, Barcelona l\u00e0 s\u1ed1t s\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111\u1ed3n r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Griezmann v\u00e0 s\u1ebd mang anh v\u1ec1 v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2018 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n ra nh\u01b0 Barca t\u1eebng mong \u0111\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00f4ng qua video h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh th\u00f4ng qua video h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/17/Griezmann-da-cong-bo-tuong-lai-cua-minh-thong-qua-video-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Europa League v\u1edbi Atletico, Griezmann b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u suy t\u00ednh l\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. C\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u tham v\u1ecdng chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n qua vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n HLV Diego Simeone c\u00f9ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng Antoine Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. N\u00f3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cho t\u1edbi c\u00e1ch th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a anh. Trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n, Griezmann b\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c s\u1ebd ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111i hay \u1edf nh\u01b0 phim bom t\u1ea5n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Griezmann va video\" title=\"Griezmann va video\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Griezmann-va-video.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M\u1ed9t c\u1ea3nh trong video c\u1ee7a Griezmann</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. Trong m\u1ed9t \u0111o\u1ea1n video \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, Griezmann kho\u00e1c t\u1ea5m \u00e1o \u0111en c\u00f3 m\u0169 tr\u00f9m \u0111\u1ee9ng trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng le l\u00f3i b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng \u00e1nh \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea7m t\u01b0 nh\u00ecn v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda m\u1ed9t s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e2u xa l\u1ea1, ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Wanda Metropolitano c\u1ee7a Atletico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e1c C\u0110V c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i, ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\u201d, Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 vi\u1ebft nh\u01b0 v\u1eady tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. \u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i. H\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef cho Atletico ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League, hy v\u1ecdng l\u00e0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 n\u0103m 2019. H\u1ecd \u0111ang n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c mang v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Antoine Griezmann tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/griezmann-la-dai-ca-o-tuyen-phap-421-188449.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/griezmann-la-dai-ca-o-tuyen-phap.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/griezmann-la-dai-ca-o-tuyen-phap-421-188449.html\">Griezmann l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i ca \u1edf tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra \u00edt ng\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Antoine Griezmann \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ca ng\u1ee3i b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh - sao tr\u1ebb Mbappe.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-griezmann-se-giup-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-188443.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/mbappe-griezmann-se-giup-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mbappe-griezmann-se-giup-phap-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-421-188443.html\">Mbappe: Griezmann s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\n<span>Kylian Mbappe ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Antoine Griezmann, ng\u00f4i sao 19 tu\u1ed5i tin r\u1eb1ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Atletico Madrid s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0110T Ph\u00e1p v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3620","checkdouble":"188510"},{"date":"06:54 15/06","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Barca n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Griezmann \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/17/nguoi-barca-noi-gi-ve-viec-griezmann-o-lai-atletico.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Pique ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Griezmann v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico Madrid c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p. Anh g\u1eedi l\u1eddi ch\u00fac m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Barcelona trong th\u1eddi gian qua s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Griezmann \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Antoine Griezmann \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ed9 l\u00ean kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edbt trong th\u1eddi gian qua. V\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Atletico Madrid ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u00f4ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong \u0111\u00f3, Barcelona l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1t khao nh\u1ea5t. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1o li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Griezmann b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 vi ph\u1ea1m quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi (FIFA). Nghe \u0111\u00e2u, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pique ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Griezmann v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pique ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Griezmann v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Pique-phat-bieu-ve-Griezmann-va-quyet-dinh-o-lai-Atletico-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Griezmann quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico th\u00f4ng qua m\u1ed9t video</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/antoine-griezmann-da-cong-bo-tuong-lai-180-188510.html\" target=\"_blank\">quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Griezmann</span> l\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico. Anh m\u1edbi c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u00f4ng qua m\u1ed9t \u0111o\u1ea1n video \u0111\u1eb7c s\u1eafc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t b\u1edfi c\u00f4ng ty \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 Kosmos c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Gerard Pique.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pique ch\u00fac Griezmann may m\u1eafn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin tr\u00ean, Pique ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Griezmann v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p. Anh c\u1ea3m \u01a1n c\u00e1c nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean c\u00f9ng tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Kosmos ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh \u0111o\u1ea1n video n\u00f3i tr\u00ean. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Barca c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean ch\u00fac Griezmann \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Griezmann ghi ban cho Atletico truoc Marseille\" title=\"Griezmann ghi ban cho Atletico truoc Marseille\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/17/griezmann-cong-bo-tuong-lai-ngay-trong-tuan-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pique ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Griezmann v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>M\u1ed9t g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eafn \u0111o c\u1ee7a Griezmann trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh</em>\u201d, Pique vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>C\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 Kosmos Studios v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Griezmann trong v\u00e0i tu\u1ea7n qua. Anh \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico v\u00e0 t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi.</em>\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, Griezmann gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung cho World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Les Blues s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi Australia v\u00e0o 17h ng\u00e0y 16/6 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Antoine Griezmann tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/messi-barca-can-griezmann-de-vo-dich-champions-league-180-188495.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/6/messi-barca-can-griezmann-de-thong-tri-chau-au.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/messi-barca-can-griezmann-de-vo-dich-champions-league-180-188495.html\">Messi: \u201cBarca c\u1ea7n Griezmann \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League\u201d</span><br>\r\n<span>\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u00f4i sao s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn x\u1ee9 Catalonia trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/griezmann-len-ke-hoach-thong-bao-tuong-lai-nhu-phim-bom-tan-180-188470.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/27/griezmann-len-ke-hoach-thong-bao-tuong-lai-nhu-phim-bom-tan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/griezmann-len-ke-hoach-thong-bao-tuong-lai-nhu-phim-bom-tan-180-188470.html\">Griezmann l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai... nh\u01b0 phim bom t\u1ea5n</span><br>\r\n<span>Sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i, c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Antoine Griemann th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa ph\u1ea3i d\u1eddi l\u1ea1i.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3619","checkdouble":"188517"},{"date":"18:14 14/06","title":"Sao Bundesliga x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool theo \u0111u\u1ed5i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/19/sao-bundesliga-xac-nhan-duoc-ca-arsenal-va-liverpool-theo-duoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Caglar Soyuncu c\u1ee7a Freiburg hi\u1ec7n th\u1eddi l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia Premier League v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Gia nh\u1eadp Freiburg t\u1eeb CLB Altinordu c\u1ee7a Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2016, Caglar Soyuncu kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc qua hai n\u0103m chinh chi\u1ebfn \u1edf Bundesliga. L\u1ee3i th\u1ebf th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao 1m87, sao tr\u1ebb sinh n\u0103m 1996 tranh ch\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean kh\u00f4ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 d\u01b0\u1edbi m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ecdc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a anh c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool tranh mua sao tr\u1ebb Soyuncu c\u1ee7a TNK h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool tranh mua sao tr\u1ebb Soyuncu c\u1ee7a TNK h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/19/Arsenal-mua-Sokratis-cua-Dortmund-voi-gia-17-trieu-bang-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool tranh mua sao tr\u1ebb Soyuncu</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool tranh mua sao tr\u1ebb Soyuncu</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi Soyuncu l\u1ecdt m\u1eaft xanh c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Premier League. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Mustafa Dogru \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i nghi\u00eam t\u00fac b\u1edfi Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool. \u00d4ng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cSven Mislintat (Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c tuy\u1ec3n tr\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a Arsenal) \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ebfn Caglar k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f2n \u1edf Dortmund. Gi\u1edd c\u0169ng v\u1eady k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi Sven \u0111\u00e3 sang Arsenal, v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng trao \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1eafc duy nh\u1ea5t c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Freiburg.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang ta s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng ch\u1edd xem nh\u1eefng di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd ra sao, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool tranh mua sao tr\u1ebb Soyuncu c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 4-5 CLB Premier League kh\u00e1c \u0111ang th\u0103m d\u00f2 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u00e0y.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed, \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Atletico Madrid hay nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Ph\u00e1p, \u0110\u1ee9c, \u00dd n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd g\u00ec v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y khi Caglar th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1eabu trung v\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, linh ho\u1ea1t, c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, thu\u1eadn hai ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i c\u1ef1c \u1ed5n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng Premier League.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-sap-co-soyuncu-cua-freiburg-172-185535.html\">L\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n danh t\u00ednh t\u00e2n binh r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/muc-tieu-35-trieu-bang-cua-arsenal-thua-nhan-muon-toi-nha-172-186635.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Arsenal th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi NHA</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-gia-co-hang-thu-bang-thuong-vu-caglar-soyuncu-172-183051.html\">Arsenal nh\u1eafm sao tr\u1ebb Bundesliga \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebf v\u1ecb cho Laurent Koscielny</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3618","checkdouble":"188492"},{"date":"18:22 14/06","title":"Napoli x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Man City chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/22/napoli-xac-nhan-man-city-chuan-bi-no-bom-tan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Aurelio De Laurentiis cho bi\u1ebft th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Etihad v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kho\u1ea3ng 70 tri\u1ec7u Euro.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u00e0 t\u00e2n v\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p khu trung tuy\u1ebfn b\u1eb1ng Jorginho trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd g\u1ed1c Brazil. Joao Santos cho bi\u1ebft th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Etihad v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u1edd ng\u00e0y Man City \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n Napoli.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City mua Jorginho th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Napoli v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man City mua Jorginho th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Napoli v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/22/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-126-MU-nhan-cu-soc-nang-trong-vu-con-trai-Kluivert-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City mua Jorginho t\u1eeb Napoli v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u Euro trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ng\u00e0y \u0111\u00f3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng s\u1eafp t\u1edbi v\u00e0 l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Aurelio De Laurentiis x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u2013 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-city-da-co-duoc-trai-tim-sao-napoli-172-188151.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City mua Jorginho</span> th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u Euro trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Serie A:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cM\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 \u1ed5n th\u1ecfa r\u1ed3i, n\u00ean t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y th\u00f4i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n duy tr\u00ec m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1edbi Man City v\u00e0 qua ti\u1ebfn tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n n\u00e0y c\u0169ng v\u1eady. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t l\u1ea1c quan v\u00e0o k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n c\u1ea3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u0103ng hoa v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a Napoli v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Serie A quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t v\u00e0 s\u00f2ng ph\u1eb3ng v\u1edbi Juventus g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn b\u1edfi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho. Thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf khu trung t\u00e2m, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd g\u1ed1c Brazil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thu h\u1ed3i v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng, ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng hay h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/napoli-xac-nhan-man-city-da-hoi-mua-jorginho-172-187592.html\">Napoli x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Man City \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecfi mua Jorginho</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-ly-do-man-city-van-chua-the-co-duoc-jorginho-172-187816.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do Man City v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Jorginho</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3617","checkdouble":"188493"},{"date":"21:21 14/06","title":"Ai C\u1eadp nh\u1eadn tin vui b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1eeb \u201cTh\u00e1nh Salah\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/ai-cap-nhan-tin-vui-bat-ngo-tu-thanh-salah.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a HLV \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp Hector Cuper, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mohamed Salah b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n ngay tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n.\r\n</h2><h2>Salah \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u1eeba qua, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Sergio Ramos h\u1ea1 \u0111o v\u00e1n b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00f2n v\u1eadt. Anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng vai v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C1, khi\u1ebfn Liverpool b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid. Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y th\u1eadm ch\u00ed khi\u1ebfn Salah b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tham d\u1ef1 World Cup.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Mohamed Salah v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi \u0110T Uruguay. D\u00f9 v\u1eady theo l\u1eddi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a HLV \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp Hector Cuper, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Salah b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, s\u1eabn s\u00e0ng t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Salah b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, s\u1eabn s\u00e0ng t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/salah.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Ai C\u1eadp x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Salah b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Cuper cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn 100% r\u1eb1ng, v\u00e2ng, Salah s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 n\u00e0o trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u00eam t\u1ef1 tin.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;C\u00e1c b\u00e1c s\u0129 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n hay kh\u00f4ng. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 t\u00ednh c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, Salah kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 s\u1ee3 h\u00e3i v\u00e0 n\u00f3ng l\u00f2ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xung tr\u1eadn. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1eb7p r\u1ee7i ro l\u1edbn, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 che gi\u1ea5u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu Salah quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u1ed5n. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd xem x\u00e9t v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1&rdquo; &ndash; HLV Cuper b\u00e1o tin m\u1eebng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Ai C\u1eadp.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mohamed Salah b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u00e2u Phi s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u1edbi Uruguay t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng A. Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c World Cup 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra gi\u1eefa <span href=\"http://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/nga-vs-saudi-arabia-khai-mac-world-cup-2018-463-188481.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nga vs Saudi Arabia</span>, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u trong nh\u1eefng l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-salah-se-canh-tranh-qbv-voi-toi-va-messi-421-188359.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/27/tai-sao-ronaldo-dong-vien-salah-khi-doi-thu-roi-san-do-chan-thuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ronaldo-salah-se-canh-tranh-qbv-voi-toi-va-messi-421-188359.html\">Ronaldo: Salah s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh QBV v\u1edbi t\u00f4i v\u00e0 Messi</span><br>\r\nRonaldo khen Salah, tin t\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u00f4i sao Liverpool s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ai C\u1eadp v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho danh hi\u1ec7u Qu\u1ea3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/salah-to-ramos-choi-tro-meo-khoc-chuot-voi-minh-184-188136.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/27/salah-to-ramos-choi-tro-meo-khoc-chuot-voi-minh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/salah-to-ramos-choi-tro-meo-khoc-chuot-voi-minh-184-188136.html\">Salah t\u1ed1 Ramos ch\u01a1i tr\u00f2 &ldquo;m\u00e8o kh\u00f3c chu\u1ed9t&rdquo; v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1p tr\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Ai C\u1eadp sau khi trung v\u1ec7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u1eafn tin h\u1ecfi th\u0103m nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00f4 can v\u1edbi pha ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a anh trong...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3616","checkdouble":"188498"},{"date":"21:39 14/06","title":"Man United chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u01b0a Gareth Bale l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u201ckh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/1/man-united-chuan-bi-dua-gareth-bale-loi-de-nghi-khong-the-tu-choi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh \u0111\u01b0a tin HLV Jose Mourinho ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o Gareth Bale, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nM.U mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Bale<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a M.U trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng si\u00eau sao, c\u00f2n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Gareth Bale sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra \u0111i. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Man United mu\u1ed1n CLB chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Bale, d\u00f9 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o \u0111i ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft, theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb t\u1edd Manchester Evening News (M.E.N) &ndash; m\u1ed9t t\u1edd b\u00e1o th\u00e2n t\u00edn c\u1ee7a 2 CLB th\u00e0nh Manchester, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e2u k\u00e9o ng\u00f4i sao x\u1ee9 Wales ngay m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh 4 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League, M.U hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn anh theo m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do M.E.N chia s\u1ebb, Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn cho Bale &ndash; th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u00ednh Real Madrid c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 tr\u00ean k\u00eanh truy\u1ec1n h\u00ecnh El Chiringuito: &ldquo;N\u1ebfu Bale \u0111\u1ebfn M.U, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o Gareth Bale v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o Gareth Bale v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/1/Mourinho-cheo-keo-Gareth-Bale-voi-loi-de-nghi-khong-the-tu-choi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o Gareth Bale b\u1eb1ng l\u1eddi h\u1ee9a Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 lu\u00f4n khao kh\u00e1t tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 1, Bale r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng cao qu\u00fd n\u00e0y d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 1 l\u1ea7n trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Nh\u01b0ng cho d\u00f9 anh th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ra sao \u1ecf Real Madrid, li\u00ean t\u1ee5c gi\u00fap CLB gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch trong 5 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i qua, th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 Bale ch\u1ec9 ch\u00ecm trong c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Man United, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh trung t\u00e2m trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Hi\u1ec7n nay, d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Alexis Sanchez, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao nh\u01b0 Gareth Bale l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u M.U c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu, n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh cho nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Mourinho ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o Gareth Bale th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng bom t\u1ea5n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/gareth-bale-sang-mu-thuong-vu-tot-cho-tat-ca-184-187216.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/28/gareth-bale-sang-mu-thuong-vu-tot-cho-tat-ca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/gareth-bale-sang-mu-thuong-vu-tot-cho-tat-ca-184-187216.html\">Gareth Bale sang MU: Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 t\u1ed1t cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3</span><br>\r\nCh\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd, HLV Jose Mourinho ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n &ldquo;gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1&rdquo; c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Gareth Bale sang MU \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u00ean to\u00e0n n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bale-la-cai-ten-6-clb-hang-dau-nuoc-anh-deu-them-khat-172-187302.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/28/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-295-mu-phai-chi-335-trieu-bang-de-co-bale.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/bale-la-cai-ten-6-clb-hang-dau-nuoc-anh-deu-them-khat-172-187302.html\">Bale l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean 6 CLB h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec1u th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t</span><br>\r\nTheo c\u1ef1u HLV Tottenham Harry Reknapp, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Gareth Bale chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Premier League s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3615","checkdouble":"188500"},{"date":"22:16 14/06","title":"Lampard c\u00f3 l\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch cho b\u00ed \u1ea9n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 c\u00f9ng Gerrard","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/14/lampard-co-loi-giai-thich-cho-bi-an-khong-the-da-cung-gerrard.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh, nh\u01b0ng Lampard chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Gerrard v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, b\u1edfi c\u1ea3 2 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00f2a h\u1ee3p trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nC\u00f3 Gerrard, th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng Lampard<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 b\u1ed9 n\u00e3o c\u1ee7a Liverpool v\u00e0 Chelsea &ndash; nh\u01b0ng 2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Steven Gerrard v\u00e0 Frank Lampard kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd ph\u00e1t huy to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh khi l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n. S\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng n\u0103m 2004 v\u00e0 2006, nh\u01b0ng vinh quang li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ngo\u1ea3nh m\u1eb7t Tam S\u01b0, khi h\u1ecd c\u1ed1 nh\u1ed3i nh\u00e9t c\u1ea3 2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-4-2.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c nh\u1eadm ch\u1ee9c HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Derby County, Frank Lampard l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i: &ldquo;Tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, t\u00f4i v\u00e0 Gerrard l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u00f3 v\u1ebb \u1ed5n l\u00fac \u0111\u1ea7u, nh\u01b0ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda v\u1ec1 sau. \u0110\u00e1ng ra ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u00ean thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.&rdquo;&nbsp;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lampard chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Gerrard Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lampard chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Gerrard Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/lampard.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lampard chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Gerrard th\u1eddi c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng nhau</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 Owen Hargreaves, Michael Carrick ho\u1eb7c Paul Scholes, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 l\u00f9i s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i M.U. T\u00f4i v\u00e0 Gerrard ch\u1eb3ng l\u00e0 g\u00ec n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi, m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7m nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 y\u00ean t\u00e2m t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. K\u1ef3 World Cup 2006 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3&rdquo; &ndash; Lampard chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Gerrard.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Th\u00fa th\u1ef1c, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia. C\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ebd theo d\u00f5i m\u1ed7i khi b\u1ea1n ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 ngu ng\u1ed1c. N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3 trung th\u1ef1c, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng s\u1ebd n\u00f3i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady&rdquo; &ndash; Lampard g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Chelsea c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o \u0110T Anh \u1edf World Cup 2018. Lampard t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi Tam S\u01b0 ch\u1ecdn s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, v\u00e0 ch\u00fac c\u00e1c \u0111\u00e0n em g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mourinho-phat-bieu-day-bat-ngo-ve-dt-anh-421-188487.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/24/mourinho-phat-bieu-day-bat-ngo-ve-dt-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/mourinho-phat-bieu-day-bat-ngo-ve-dt-anh-421-188487.html\">Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, HLV Jose Mourinho d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh v\u1edbi l\u1eddi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-tai-world-cup-421-188300.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/12/harry-kane-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-tai-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-tai-world-cup-421-188300.html\">Harry Kane \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea1i World Cup</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y n\u1eefa l\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Harry Kane mu\u1ed1n \u0110T Anh l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh &ndash; TTVN</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3614","checkdouble":"188501"},{"date":"13:24 14/06","title":"D\u00e0n tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 \u0111ang b\u1ecb h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t ch\u00e2n d\u00e0i \"c\u00e1m d\u1ed7\"","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/14/dan-tuyen-thu-anh-du-world-cup-2018-dang-bi-hang-loat-chan-dai-cam-do.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p s\u1ed1ng g\u1ea7n kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u1edf World Cup \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Tam s\u01b0.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Th\u00f4ng tin h\u00e9 l\u1ed9 t\u1eeb \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng h\u1eb9n h\u00f2 Tinder cho th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t ch\u00e2n d\u00e0i h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t trong v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u00ednh 10km c\u1ee7a n\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nC\u00f4 g\u00e1i t\u00f3c v\u00e0ng 21 tu\u1ed5i Alexis chia s\u1ebb \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm &quot;m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n cho \u0111\u1ebfn khi World Cup k\u1ebft th\u00fac&quot;. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p 26 tu\u1ed5i Zhanna khoe \u1ea3nh th\u01b0\u1edbt tha v\u1edbi v\u00e1y tr\u1eafng v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i th\u00f4ng tin c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n tr\u00ean \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng Tinder. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u c\u01b0 tr\u00fa t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n ForRestMix kh\u00f4ng xa.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 \u0111ang b\u1ecb h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t ch\u00e2n d\u00e0i d\u1ee5 d\u1ed7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 \u0111ang b\u1ecb h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t ch\u00e2n d\u00e0i d\u1ee5 d\u1ed7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/cc-7505-1528947857.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">C\u00e1c ch\u00e2n d\u00e0i g\u1ea7n kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u0103ng \u1ea3nh mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u1ea1n trai tr\u00ean \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng Tinder. \u1ea2nh: NS.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTinder ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u1edf Nga - qu\u1ed1c gia c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 &quot;thi\u1ebfu h\u1ee5t&quot; c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng. Ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch gi\u1edbi t\u00ednh nam v\u00e0 n\u1eef l\u00ean t\u1edbi 11 tri\u1ec7u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eef nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. S\u1ef1 m\u1ea5t c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng x\u1ea3y ra nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u1edf Saint Petersburg, c\u00e1ch n\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u00f4ng xa. \u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng h\u00e8n h\u00f2 cho ph\u00e9p s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb GPS \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm b\u1ea1n kh\u00e1c gi\u1edbi g\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh nh\u1ea5t.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay, HLV Southgate kh\u00e1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ee3, b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i \u0111i c\u00f9ng. Tuy v\u1eady, kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i ban h\u00e0nh l\u1ec7nh c\u1ea5m s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng h\u1eb9n h\u00f2 tr\u1ef1c tuy\u1ebfn v\u01a1i tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Anh hay kh\u00f4ng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&quot;Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Gareth mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o World Cup. M\u1ea5t th\u1eddi gian v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u00f4 g\u00e1i \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ean c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng h\u1eb9n h\u00f2 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m suy y\u1ebfu tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 g\u00e2y ra r\u1ee7i ro an ninh \u1edf Nga&quot;, m\u1ed9t ngu\u1ed3n tin cho bi\u1ebft.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u1ede kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n \u0111\u00f3ng qu\u00e2n, tuy\u1ec3n Anh l\u00e0m h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o cao, c\u00e1ch ly \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n v\u1edbi b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i. Vi\u1ec7c ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t an ninh c\u0169ng di\u1ec5n ra g\u1eaft gao b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng lo ng\u1ea1i v\u00ec v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb gi\u1eefa hai n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3613","checkdouble":"188472"},{"date":"17:36 14/06","title":"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i V-League: \u0110\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac ngh\u0129 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/ha-noi-dai-thang-tai-vleague-da-den-luc-nghi-nghiem-tuc-ve-san-choi-chau-luc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua, c\u00e1c CLB Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn xem th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111em \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, khi m\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111ang ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i V-League, xem ch\u1eebng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 c\u00e1i nh\u00ecn m\u1edbi v\u1ec1 AFC Cup.</h2><h2>B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng th\u1ee5t l\u00f9i v\u00ec t\u01b0 duy c\u0169</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi nay, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng t\u1ecf ra &lsquo;m\u1eb7n&rsquo; v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea5p CLB nh\u01b0 AFC Champions League hay AFC Cup m\u00e0 l\u00fd do ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 chinh chi\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t l\u00fac tr\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i AFC Cup n\u0103m nay, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t SLNA thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c hay \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean nh\u01b0ng c\u00e0ng v\u1ec1 cu\u1ed1i, s\u1ef1 h\u1ee5t h\u01a1i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 khi h\u1ecd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague-c291-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">V-League</span>.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i V-League \u0110\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 AFC Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i V-League \u0110\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 AFC Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/30/Ha-Noi-bat-bai-tai-V-League-Da-den-luc-nghi-ve-AFC-Cup-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0 SLNA \u0111\u1ec1u d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng AFC Cup 2018.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c s\u1edbm bu\u00f4ng AFC Cup l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn hai CLB Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 FLC Thanh H\u00f3a v\u00e0 SLNA \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua n\u1ed5i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong khu v\u1ef1c, d\u00f9 x\u00e9t tr\u00ean b\u00ecnh di\u1ec7n \u0110TQG th\u00ec b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e0nh t\u00edch thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e3 mang t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 kh\u00e1 tai h\u1ea1i l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t khi ch\u00fang ta \u0111ang ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng th\u1ee5t l\u00f9i tr\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00ec n\u1ebfp suy ngh\u0129 c\u0169. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n th\u1eddi m\u1ed9t B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eebng tung ho\u00e0nh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i Champions League hay AFC Cup, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t nh\u1ee3t nh\u1ea1t c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1ea7m khu v\u1ef1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e1ng gi\u1ec1ng Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ec7m c\u1eadn c\u00e1c n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 nh\u01b0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Trung Qu\u1ed1c, H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Iran,&hellip; v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ea1ng 8 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng th\u1ee9 19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1, x\u1ebfp d\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ea3 Malaysia hay Philippines, hai qu\u1ed1c gia v\u1ed1n \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean ti\u1ebfng vang t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u b\u1edfi trong nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m qua, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n n\u00e0o ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng AFC Cup, ch\u1ee9 ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i t\u1edbi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea1ng 1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 l\u00e0 AFC Champions League.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"AFC Club Ranking\" title=\"AFC Club Ranking\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Thai-Lan-vuot-Australia-bo-xa-Viet-Nam-tren-BXH-chau-a-vn-02-1528445203-width709height633.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5p \u1edf c\u1ea5p CLB</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u0169ng t\u1eebng su\u00fdt v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng AFC Cup 2017 v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ebb tre \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, tuy nhi\u00ean sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd 2-6 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Ceres-Negros, t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 duy nh\u1ea5t b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong tay h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u0103m nay, v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i V-League 2018, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng AFC Cup 2019. V\u00e0 thi\u1ebft ngh\u0129 l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eb1m gi\u00fap b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00e2ng cao th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c c\u1ea5p CLB.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u t\u1ea1i AFC Cup l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/dtqg-c292-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span> t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1, c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u0169ng&nbsp;\u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 chuy\u1ec3n m\u00ecnh v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. Thi \u0111\u1ea5u chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p h\u01a1n, tin d\u00f9ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u00e0 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft, hoa m\u0129 h\u01a1n, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i V-League kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m g\u00ec s\u1ee9c h\u00fat c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u00e0 b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean khi m\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2y, CLB HAGL v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn th\u00ec r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 c\u0169ng gi\u00e0u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi th\u1ed1 \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ha Noi vs Than Quang Ninh Oseni\" title=\"H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh Oseni\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/oseni-5816-1528894838_600x0.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ecdi \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn xa \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i V-League nh\u1edd \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. L\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00fac n\u00e0y l\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111ang \u1edf trong \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng b\u1ea7u r\u1ee7ng r\u1ec9nh v\u1ec1 t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ee9ng sau ch\u1ed1ng l\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec3 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00f3 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf AFC Cup.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u1ed9t m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 chu\u1ea9n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb c\u00f3 d\u1ecbp tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 t\u00edch l\u0169y ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c, kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u1ec3 qua \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 CLB v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0110TQG sau n\u00e0y. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cao t\u1ea1i VCK Asian Cup 2019 v\u00e0 xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 k\u1ef3 World Cup 2026.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u1ea5t. V\u00e0 r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u0169ng \u0111ang chung tay x\u00e2y \u0111\u1eafp \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam-c168-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span> t\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u01b0\u01a1n cao nh\u1eb1m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ec7m c\u1eadn tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/13/Ha-Noi-4-1-Quang-Ninh.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hagl-thua-quang-nam-tat-ca-da-nam-trong-toan-tinh-cua-bau-duc-168-188433.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/23/hagl-thua-quang-nam-tat-ca-da-nam-trong-toan-tinh-cua-bau-duc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hagl-thua-quang-nam-tat-ca-da-nam-trong-toan-tinh-cua-bau-duc-168-188433.html\">HAGL thua Qu\u1ea3ng Nam: T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eb1m trong toan t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c</span><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecf ra bi quan v\u1ec1 ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a CLB HAGL sau tr\u1eadn thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i qua t\u1ea1i Pleiku. Tuy nhi\u00ean...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/ha-noi-fc-mung-sinh-nhat-tuoi-12-day-y-nghia-291-188432.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/ha-noi-fc-mung-sinh-nhat-tuoi-12-day-y-nghia.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/ha-noi-fc-mung-sinh-nhat-tuoi-12-day-y-nghia-291-188432.html\">Ch\u00f9m \u1ea3nh: M\u00e0n ch\u00fac m\u1eebng sinh nh\u1eadt tu\u1ed5i 12 c\u1ef1c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC</span><br>\r\nH\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC m\u1eebng sinh nh\u1eadt tu\u1ed5i 12 \u0111\u1ea7y \u00fd ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi m\u00e0n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f4ng phu c\u1ee7a h\u1ed9i c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ha-noi-nhan-thuong-khung-tu-bau-hien-sau-chien-tich-bat-bai-o-luot-di-168-188427.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/16/ha-noi-nhan-thuong-khung-tu-bau-hien-sau-chien-tich-bat-bai-o-luot-di.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ha-noi-nhan-thuong-khung-tu-bau-hien-sau-chien-tich-bat-bai-o-luot-di-168-188427.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i nh\u1eadn th\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u1ee7ng t\u1eeb b\u1ea7u Hi\u1ec3n sau chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u0103ng hoa c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1ea7u Hi\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n khen ng\u1ee3i v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1edfng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p>Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3612","checkdouble":"188434"}]}
